CustomMetadata.label: MFS failed to create the Prgms Amendment

values.value: There was an error in creating the MFS Mx affiliate programs and/or Store partnership records. Please refer to the error message for further details and retry in a few minutes. If issue persists, raise a support ticket - MX Finance board (https://doordash.atlassian.net/secure/CreateIssue.jspa?pid=13864&issuetype=1&priority=4) and slack on #eng-mx-finance channel :(https://app.slack.com/client/E02180LFT96/CUT5HLH2P).
